  "contentHtml": "\n                                    \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/12345678/Reuters\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Reuters</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Jul 16, 2026 at 07:49 AM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p><a href=\"/tag/icici+prudential+life+insurance\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ICICI Prudential Life Insurance</a> posted a 27.8% rise in <a href=\"/tag/first-quarter+profit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">first-quarter profit</a> on Wednesday, helped by strong growth in new business premiums and <a href=\"/tag/retail+term+insurance\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">retail term insurance</a> sales, sending its shares up as much as 5.5%.The <a href=\"/tag/value+of+new+business\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">value of new business</a>, or VNB, seen ‌as a ⁠key measure ⁠of profitability from new policies, rose 24.9% from a year earlier, easing concerns over margin pressure from goods and services tax-related input tax credit issues.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>Analysts had been watching whether ICICI Prudential Life's shift towards higher-margin non-participating and retail term insurance products would ​offset those headwinds.</p>\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>Annualised premium equivalent sales, ⁠a key ‌measure of new business, rose 14.6% to ​21.36 billion ​rupees ($221.9 million), while the VNB margin improved ⁠to 26.7% from 24.5% a year earlier.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>Investors and ​analysts closely watch these operational metrics to ​gauge the health of new business for insurers.Prudential has said it must cut its stake in the Indian insurer to below 10%, from about 22%, to secure regulatory approval for its planned 75% acquisition of Bharti Axa ‌Life Insurance, which was announced in May.Bernstein analysts have warned that the resulting sale of nearly ​a 12% ​stake could create ⁠a supply overhang and weigh on ICICI Prudential Life's shares.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>On Wednesday, its board approved a proposal to rename the company to ​ICICI Life Insurance Limited. Its shares closed up 3.78% at 523 rupees.Peers HDFC Life Insurance and SBI Life Insurance have yet to report their quarterly results.($1 = 96.2475 Indian rupees)                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                    \n\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/12345678/Reuters\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Reuters</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Jul 16, 2026 at 07:49 AM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Jul 16, 2026 at 07:49 AM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                                            \n                                        <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n            <!-- <figure class=\"top-newsletter-subs__icon-nl\" role=\"presentation\" aria-label=\"Newsletter icon\">\n                <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-newsletter.svg\" alt=\"Newsletter icon\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\">\n            </figure> -->\n        \n            \n                \n                    <h2>All about ETHealthworld industry right on your smartphone! </h2>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"/app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download the ETHealthworld App</a> and get the Realtime updates and Save your favourite articles.</li>\n                    </ul>\n                                            <!-- <div class=\"app-store-container desktop-view\">\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"\" aria-label=\"Play Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-g-play.png\" alt=\"\" />\n                            </a>\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"App Store\">\n                            